{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which was-- which was sympathetic to the Jews, and one was not sympathetic to the   Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Armia Krajowa definitely was not, and Armia Ludowa seemingly supposed to have the sympathetic to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of an inspection of Germans coming to the village to stuff us in into that things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really not made for 10 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just barely-- when we had to go in there, it was really that we could stand one against the other in a standing position.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's about all-- also, no air whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, when-- that night that I was watching, I did see some really fire, pieces of bumps, so to say.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I could hear it, swishes coming into the fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I really did not know, or I did not experience that kind of fightings, or anything of approaching an army, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do I do I do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I walked over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The man was sleeping in that room where I was sitting at the window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I woke him up, and I called him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I barely touched him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was afraid that he may hit me by waking in middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, 'Mister, Mister, I-- I see some fire falling in our fields.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know what it is.' He says, 'Good, good, you woke me up.' I said, 'I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].' 'No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's good, it's good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You did right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You did right.' He walks out-- get dressed, walks out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, 'The Russians are closing in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The front is here.'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, 'Tell everybody to get dressed, whatever it is, because I want you to get into the barn and into the cellar.' So we went into the barn and cellar.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
